item.title: GitFixPushError
item.author: tedliuzy@hotmail.com (TED LZY)
item.description: The error message you’re encountering indicates that your local master branch is behind the remote master branch on GitHub. To resolve this issue, you need to update your local branch with the changes from the remote branch before you can push your changes.
